description: Cheech A' Cini's Italian Grill is thrilling the foodies of Staten Island with their incredibly tasty and authentic gourmet Italian street cuisine.  Their menu offers a unique twist on classic Italian favorites, all made with sustainable ingredients, and all quite delicious. A few items you'll find include their savory Grilled Chicken Veggie Panini, the oh-so-robust Meatball Burger, their golden fried Pasta Balls, and much more. Next time you’re feeling hungry, just follow the Italian flag and order up a flavorful meal from Cheech A' Cini's.
name: Cheech A' Cini's Italian Grill
